Interface IPositionSnapped

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAttachable, IGeoCoordinate, IPosition, IPositionOffset, com.tractrac.util.lib.api.serialize.ISerializable, ITimeData

    public interface IPositionSnapped
extends IPosition, IPositionOffset
    A snapped position is a position along a line or a route. On top of the underlying position it also provides the offset from the start of the line or route.
